{
  "name": "scrabblescorer",
  "type": "module",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "A program that accepts user input in the form of a word and returns a Scrabble score relative to one of three scoring algorithms.\r * The first algorithm, \"Scrabble\" awards points relative to the letter's rarity.\r * The second algorithm, \"Simple Score\" awards one point for every letter.\r * The third algorithm, \"Bonus Vowels\" awards three points for vowels, one point for consonants.",
